cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques to predict user ratings and reviews for products or services. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to gather and analyze existing reviews and ratings, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely sub-category. The use of neural networks for multi-task joint learning suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
